1
00:00:22,986 --> 00:00:28,976
♪Remembering the old days in a trance♪

2
00:00:29,326 --> 00:00:36,136
♪We are destined to fight together♪

3
00:00:36,416 --> 00:00:43,116
♪The past has gone but the memory lasts♪

4
00:00:43,436 --> 00:00:50,456
♪Our happiness and sorrow
in the good old days♪

5
00:00:50,666 --> 00:00:57,296
♪The journey is difficult,
through the crowds, to the end of time♪

6
00:00:57,616 --> 00:01:05,816
♪I'm brave and undefeatable♪

7
00:01:06,536 --> 00:01:13,566
♪The sky has become dark
and the birds have returned home♪

8
00:01:13,726 --> 00:01:20,776
♪Breaking all obstacles
and reaching the peak above the clouds♪

9
00:01:20,926 --> 00:01:27,776
♪Watching the thin plumes of smoke
and the beautiful scenery♪

10
00:01:27,936 --> 00:01:31,246
♪Working together,
overcoming all difficulties♪

11
00:01:31,516 --> 00:01:35,676
♪I will be known as the fearless one♪

12
00:01:35,676 --> 00:01:39,796
=Douluo Continent=

13
00:01:39,876 --> 00:01:42,836
=Episode 22=

14
00:01:44,438 --> 00:01:45,237
After the mutation,

15
00:01:45,678 --> 00:01:47,477
the force behind the Fiend Battle Team found me.

16
00:01:47,797 --> 00:01:48,398
They told me

17
00:01:49,237 --> 00:01:51,318
that whoever works alone will be bullied.

18
00:01:51,398 --> 00:01:52,597
But if we stick together,

19
00:01:53,157 --> 00:01:53,837
it will be different.

20
00:01:55,597 --> 00:01:57,318
If we are united

21
00:01:58,398 --> 00:01:59,157
and help each other,

22
00:01:59,638 --> 00:02:01,078
our fates could be changed.

23
00:02:01,438 --> 00:02:03,078
That's why you joined the Fiend Battle Team?

24
00:02:04,038 --> 00:02:04,477
Yes.

25
00:02:05,958 --> 00:02:08,998
I can't compare myself to Master Ye.

26
00:02:09,557 --> 00:02:11,477
I can only practice hard
in the Fiend Battle Team first.

27
00:02:12,277 --> 00:02:13,837
After hearing from Master Ye

28
00:02:14,197 --> 00:02:15,318
that you would come to have a test,

29
00:02:16,157 --> 00:02:17,157
I was extremely excited.

30
00:02:18,237 --> 00:02:19,157
I have been waiting for you.

31
00:02:19,918 --> 00:02:21,198
But I heard that the Fiend Battle Team

32
00:02:21,478 --> 00:02:22,918
killed many people in the Soul Arena.

33
00:02:23,157 --> 00:02:24,038
We couldn't help it.

34
00:02:24,717 --> 00:02:25,717
It was because they were weak.

35
00:02:25,997 --> 00:02:27,118
Why didn't you just drive them away

36
00:02:27,318 --> 00:02:28,357
instead of killing them?

37
00:02:29,198 --> 00:02:30,118
Our captain said

38
00:02:30,558 --> 00:02:32,637
that we shouldn't spare anyone in a battle.

39
00:02:33,198 --> 00:02:35,077
We should spread the fear,

40
00:02:35,597 --> 00:02:37,318
and no one would dare to question us.

41
00:02:38,877 --> 00:02:39,877
It is too cruel.

42
00:02:40,838 --> 00:02:41,717
But it is very effective.

43
00:02:44,558 --> 00:02:45,437
Under the leadership of the captain,

44
00:02:46,118 --> 00:02:46,877
soon Xi Si City

45
00:02:47,678 --> 00:02:49,597
will be a territory of the Fiend Battle Team.

46
00:02:54,517 --> 00:02:55,797
I know what you are worrying about.

47
00:02:56,958 --> 00:02:57,678
In our team,

48
00:02:58,157 --> 00:02:59,877
there are a few Soul Masters
with Quadruple Soul Rings

49
00:03:00,558 --> 00:03:01,437
that you can't defeat.

50
00:03:01,838 --> 00:03:04,038
But since you're introduced by Master Ye,

51
00:03:04,758 --> 00:03:05,997
the battle

52
00:03:06,118 --> 00:03:07,597
will be just a symbolic test.

53
00:03:09,478 --> 00:03:10,958
As long as you can endure it for a while,

54
00:03:12,398 --> 00:03:13,478
you can pass the test.

55
00:03:13,717 --> 00:03:14,558
Not much risk.

56
00:03:16,558 --> 00:03:17,558
Why did you go

57
00:03:17,958 --> 00:03:18,597
to that alley?

58
00:03:19,838 --> 00:03:20,558
The woman

59
00:03:21,157 --> 00:03:22,478
is the wife of a defeated Soul Master.

60
00:03:23,437 --> 00:03:24,558
The captain asked me to throw her out of the city.

61
00:03:25,278 --> 00:03:26,637
And I happened to meet you.

62
00:03:27,678 --> 00:03:29,118
That's fine. I will deal with her later.

63
00:03:30,758 --> 00:03:32,077
She's just an ordinary person.

64
00:03:33,318 --> 00:03:35,958
You're right. I won't kill her.

65
00:03:36,918 --> 00:03:37,357
Wang Sheng.

66
00:03:37,838 --> 00:03:39,318
I can understand

67
00:03:39,318 --> 00:03:40,357
that you were tortured by Young Master Xiao.

68
00:03:41,198 --> 00:03:42,758
But you have no right
to impose your pains on others

69
00:03:43,038 --> 00:03:44,877
just as Xiao Chen Yu did to you.

70
00:03:47,118 --> 00:03:48,997
Have you forgotten that you were wanted?

71
00:03:49,278 --> 00:03:50,278
You were bullied as well.

72
00:03:50,838 --> 00:03:51,717
Someone told me

73
00:03:52,517 --> 00:03:53,597
that good people might do something wrong.

74
00:03:54,038 --> 00:03:55,118
Bad people might do something good.

75
00:03:55,478 --> 00:03:56,318
Be rational.

76
00:03:57,918 --> 00:03:58,797
The captain told me

77
00:03:59,637 --> 00:04:00,997
people who treat me nicely are good.

78
00:04:01,357 --> 00:04:02,318
Otherwise, they are all bad.

79
00:04:02,558 --> 00:04:03,597
So you want to kill them all?

80
00:04:04,157 --> 00:04:05,237
If you are so merciless,

81
00:04:05,437 --> 00:04:06,758
you are no different

82
00:04:06,758 --> 00:04:07,398
from those people who you hate a lot.

83
00:04:07,517 --> 00:04:07,958
It's enough!

84
00:04:13,797 --> 00:04:14,237
Tang San.

85
00:04:15,398 --> 00:04:16,118
Don't let our captain

86
00:04:16,517 --> 00:04:17,318
hear what you said.

87
00:04:18,278 --> 00:04:18,797
It's for your own good.

88
00:04:19,357 --> 00:04:21,357
Wang Sheng, I think

89
00:04:21,478 --> 00:04:22,038
you're not on the right track.

90
00:04:23,438 --> 00:04:25,958
You aren't going to do the test?

91
00:04:26,517 --> 00:04:27,158
I will attend

92
00:04:27,678 --> 00:04:28,357
the battle.

93
00:04:33,037 --> 00:04:33,598
That's great.

94
00:04:37,037 --> 00:04:37,917
What if I don't attend?

95
00:04:40,797 --> 00:04:41,438
Don't you know

96
00:04:42,757 --> 00:04:43,278
your matter

97
00:04:43,998 --> 00:04:45,757
is personally handled by Master Ye?

98
00:04:47,197 --> 00:04:47,998
The captain takes it seriously too.

99
00:04:49,637 --> 00:04:51,878
If you don't turn up in the battle,

100
00:04:52,197 --> 00:04:54,237
I think that the captain will lead the team

101
00:04:54,797 --> 00:04:55,317
to arrest you.

102
00:04:56,678 --> 00:04:57,678
And kill me?

103
00:04:59,598 --> 00:05:00,917
Since you've stayed,

104
00:05:01,598 --> 00:05:02,757
then we're comrades now.

105
00:05:03,517 --> 00:05:04,317
Don't think too much.

106
00:05:04,838 --> 00:05:06,237
Tomorrow the captain and I

107
00:05:06,718 --> 00:05:08,278
will bring you to the Soul Arena.

108
00:05:09,278 --> 00:05:10,637
I'm sending a group of people
out of the city tomorrow.

109
00:05:12,357 --> 00:05:13,077
Are you escaping?

110
00:05:14,838 --> 00:05:15,398
I won't.

111
00:05:16,598 --> 00:05:18,598
I've been waiting for the battle for a long time.

112
00:05:19,558 --> 00:05:21,357
It's good then. As long as
you don't escape,

113
00:05:22,158 --> 00:05:23,558
your friends, including Wu,

114
00:05:23,838 --> 00:05:24,558
will be all right.

115
00:05:26,718 --> 00:05:28,398
You mean that if I try to escape,

116
00:05:29,037 --> 00:05:30,197
you're going to hurt them?

117
00:05:31,398 --> 00:05:33,797
The captain values you a lot.

118
00:05:35,197 --> 00:05:38,357
Who only knows how to kill people
is the worst Soul Master.

119
00:05:42,477 --> 00:05:45,197
Tang San, mind your words!

120
00:05:51,598 --> 00:05:54,718
Anyway, once the battle is over tomorrow,

121
00:05:55,558 --> 00:05:56,398
we will be on the same team.

122
00:05:57,237 --> 00:05:59,797
Stop saying the words that
you mentioned just now.

123
00:06:12,917 --> 00:06:14,477
How do you feel? Do you get enough rest?

124
00:06:15,237 --> 00:06:17,517
I can still sleep for another day.

125
00:06:17,958 --> 00:06:18,438
I can accompany you.

126
00:06:18,438 --> 00:06:18,757
Don't waste the time.

127
00:06:18,757 --> 00:06:19,398
I don't want your company.

128
00:06:19,517 --> 00:06:21,037
Let's go to Tian Dou City.

129
00:06:21,678 --> 00:06:21,998
Okay.

130
00:06:21,998 --> 00:06:22,517
Headmaster.

131
00:06:23,757 --> 00:06:24,197
What's the matter?

132
00:06:25,838 --> 00:06:26,757
I send you guys off the city.

133
00:06:27,517 --> 00:06:29,757
Brother San, what do you mean by that?

134
00:06:30,037 --> 00:06:30,678
You are not leaving?

135
00:06:31,398 --> 00:06:32,037
I have to stay.

136
00:06:32,517 --> 00:06:33,598
Why?

137
00:06:35,438 --> 00:06:36,718
I have a very important matter

138
00:06:37,477 --> 00:06:38,917
to do in Xi Si City.

139
00:06:39,757 --> 00:06:41,237
What is the matter that makes you leave us?

140
00:06:41,438 --> 00:06:42,037
Brother San.

141
00:06:42,118 --> 00:06:42,517
Yes.

142
00:06:42,558 --> 00:06:43,917
We're the Seven Devils of Shi Lan Ke.

143
00:06:44,517 --> 00:06:45,718
We're all here for you.

144
00:06:45,797 --> 00:06:46,438
We will deal with it together.

145
00:06:46,678 --> 00:06:47,237
That's right.

146
00:06:47,357 --> 00:06:48,197
We can help you.

147
00:06:48,197 --> 00:06:48,878
Thank you, everyone.

148
00:06:49,517 --> 00:06:51,878
But I want to solve
the problem by myself.

149
00:06:52,278 --> 00:06:53,237
I don't want to trouble you.

150
00:06:53,958 --> 00:06:54,637
You're right.

151
00:06:55,037 --> 00:06:57,197
We shouldn't involve
Brother Dai and the others in it.

152
00:06:57,517 --> 00:06:58,958
So, let them leave on their own.

153
00:06:59,237 --> 00:07:00,197
And I'll stay with you.

154
00:07:01,637 --> 00:07:02,158
Wu,

155
00:07:02,797 --> 00:07:04,357
you have to go to Tian Dou City with them.

156
00:07:04,797 --> 00:07:06,197
There are the best Soul Masters and resources.

157
00:07:06,317 --> 00:07:07,158
This is not negotiable.

158
00:07:07,678 --> 00:07:09,398
Wu will always stay where Tang San is.

159
00:07:09,718 --> 00:07:11,317
No matter where you choose to go,

160
00:07:11,878 --> 00:07:12,958
I'll always be with you.

161
00:07:15,838 --> 00:07:16,637
You've already decided?

162
00:07:18,477 --> 00:07:19,278
I've already decided.

163
00:07:20,517 --> 00:07:21,197
What do you think?

164
00:07:25,718 --> 00:07:26,678
Shi Lan Ke School

165
00:07:27,037 --> 00:07:28,517
has been poor since its establishment.

166
00:07:29,158 --> 00:07:31,438
But I'm proud of one thing.

167
00:07:32,197 --> 00:07:34,517
Apart from giving you knowledge and power,

168
00:07:35,477 --> 00:07:37,998
we teach you how to develop
your independent personalities.

169
00:07:40,237 --> 00:07:41,118
So, Tang San,

170
00:07:42,398 --> 00:07:43,998
no matter what your decision is,

171
00:07:44,637 --> 00:07:45,998
the school will always support you.

172
00:07:48,037 --> 00:07:49,878
Headmaster, even if I leave,

173
00:07:50,357 --> 00:07:51,998
I will always be a member of Shi Lan Ke.

174
00:07:52,678 --> 00:07:53,558
Me too.

175
00:07:53,757 --> 00:07:55,158
I will always be a member of Shi Lan Ke too.

176
00:07:57,037 --> 00:07:59,718
Master, I'm always your student.

177
00:08:02,398 --> 00:08:03,477
What do you mean by that?

178
00:08:03,838 --> 00:08:04,917
Of course, you're my student.

179
00:08:05,398 --> 00:08:06,838
I won't leave you alone.

180
00:08:07,438 --> 00:08:07,878
Master...

181
00:08:07,917 --> 00:08:09,197
Okay. That's it.

182
00:08:10,158 --> 00:08:11,037
Let's

183
00:08:13,398 --> 00:08:14,398
send everyone off now.

184
00:08:29,998 --> 00:08:30,718
Master,

185
00:08:31,477 --> 00:08:33,037
do you want to leave Brother San here?

186
00:08:35,197 --> 00:08:36,398
Every one of you in Shi Lan Ke

187
00:08:36,477 --> 00:08:37,718
will leave one day.

188
00:08:38,278 --> 00:08:39,478
Do you want Shi Lan Ke

189
00:08:39,838 --> 00:08:41,197
to keep you forever?

190
00:08:43,877 --> 00:08:44,877
But you're an exception.

191
00:08:45,197 --> 00:08:46,958
You have to pay the debt you owed the school first

192
00:08:46,958 --> 00:08:47,677
before you graduate.

193
00:08:48,077 --> 00:08:48,598
I...

194
00:08:49,398 --> 00:08:51,158
Master, I'm your direct disciple.

195
00:08:52,158 --> 00:08:54,158
I can consider reducing the interest.

196
00:09:00,757 --> 00:09:01,437
Brother Dai,

197
00:09:01,798 --> 00:09:03,197
why does Tang San have to stay?

198
00:09:05,437 --> 00:09:06,197
He has his reason

199
00:09:06,958 --> 00:09:08,038
not to tell it.

200
00:09:08,877 --> 00:09:10,358
Everyone has his secrets.

201
00:09:11,117 --> 00:09:12,077
It's unnecessary to figure out the answer.

202
00:09:13,197 --> 00:09:13,997
Just believe him.

203
00:09:17,317 --> 00:09:18,517
You don't need our help?

204
00:09:19,598 --> 00:09:21,317
No. I'm okay to do it alone.

205
00:09:26,038 --> 00:09:26,718
All right.

206
00:09:27,278 --> 00:09:28,317
We're leaving the city soon.

207
00:09:28,997 --> 00:09:29,918
Just leave us here.

208
00:09:42,197 --> 00:09:44,718
All right. Continue your journey now.

209
00:09:45,077 --> 00:09:46,278
Hopefully, we will

210
00:09:47,038 --> 00:09:47,997
meet again in Tian Dou City.

211
00:09:52,077 --> 00:09:52,637
Tang San.

212
00:09:55,598 --> 00:09:57,278
Come to me whenever you encounter any problems.

213
00:09:58,798 --> 00:10:00,358
I'm always your headmaster.

214
00:10:05,958 --> 00:10:06,557
Brother San.

215
00:10:09,398 --> 00:10:10,798
What happened? Stop crying.

216
00:10:10,877 --> 00:10:11,877
Keep in mind what I've told you.

217
00:10:13,197 --> 00:10:15,637
Never give up easily.

218
00:10:19,557 --> 00:10:20,557
Take care, Brother.

219
00:10:30,077 --> 00:10:30,637
All right.

220
00:10:33,598 --> 00:10:34,718
What are you doing?

221
00:10:36,238 --> 00:10:38,637
Why didn't you tell us in advance?

222
00:10:39,117 --> 00:10:41,197
You leave us suddenly.

223
00:10:42,358 --> 00:10:43,958
How can I accept it?

224
00:10:50,238 --> 00:10:51,798
We'll meet again.

225
00:10:52,158 --> 00:10:54,478
Wu, tell us

226
00:10:55,117 --> 00:10:55,997
whenever you need our help.

227
00:10:58,517 --> 00:10:59,437
All right.

228
00:10:59,437 --> 00:11:00,437
Don't be sad.

229
00:11:01,517 --> 00:11:02,877
You meet and you depart.

230
00:11:02,877 --> 00:11:04,478
You depart and you will meet again.

231
00:11:05,038 --> 00:11:06,997
You will leave Shi Lan Ke one day.

232
00:11:07,677 --> 00:11:09,677
There is a bigger stage waiting for you.

233
00:11:10,677 --> 00:11:11,278
Stop crying.

234
00:11:12,598 --> 00:11:13,158
Let's depart now.

235
00:11:18,918 --> 00:11:19,557
Let's go.

236
00:11:20,278 --> 00:11:21,038
Take care of yourself.

237
00:11:21,038 --> 00:11:21,757
Take care, Brother Dai.

238
00:11:34,317 --> 00:11:35,918
I asked you to leave with them.

239
00:11:36,517 --> 00:11:38,718
Look at yourself now.

240
00:11:39,677 --> 00:11:40,718
That's different.

241
00:11:41,437 --> 00:11:42,238
What is the difference?

242
00:11:43,958 --> 00:11:46,598
Surely, I'll be sad when I leave them.

243
00:11:47,517 --> 00:11:48,677
But you're different.

244
00:11:48,958 --> 00:11:50,398
I can't be separated from you.

245
00:11:51,637 --> 00:11:52,757
Why can't you be separated from me?

246
00:11:54,358 --> 00:11:55,317
If I'm separated from you,

247
00:11:55,877 --> 00:11:57,718
my heart seems to be emptied.

248
00:11:58,997 --> 00:12:01,077
But, no one can stay with another forever.

249
00:12:02,557 --> 00:12:03,757
We can try.

250
00:12:07,877 --> 00:12:09,877
All right. We'll try.

251
00:12:11,557 --> 00:12:12,238
Don't cry anymore.

252
00:12:16,478 --> 00:12:18,358
Cheer up, everyone!

253
00:12:18,958 --> 00:12:20,077
Tang San said

254
00:12:20,317 --> 00:12:22,077
we might have the chance
to meet in Tian Dou City.

255
00:12:22,997 --> 00:12:23,877
Cheer up!

256
00:12:26,798 --> 00:12:28,117
Hello. May I know

257
00:12:28,197 --> 00:12:29,637
where Xi Si City Soul Arena is?

258
00:12:34,677 --> 00:12:35,598
As you mentioned,

259
00:12:35,877 --> 00:12:37,398
you have to challenge the Fiend Battle Team

260
00:12:37,677 --> 00:12:38,838
in Xi Si City Soul Arena?

261
00:12:39,398 --> 00:12:41,197
Yes, when we were at Star Town,

262
00:12:41,197 --> 00:12:41,997
Ye Zhi Qiu told me

263
00:12:42,278 --> 00:12:43,557
I could only meet with Hao Tian Soul Master

264
00:12:44,117 --> 00:12:45,598
after I had managed to defeat
the Fiend Battle Team.

265
00:12:47,557 --> 00:12:48,478
Hao Tian Soul Master

266
00:12:49,317 --> 00:12:50,677
is probably my father.

267
00:12:52,718 --> 00:12:55,437
All right. I will challenge

268
00:12:55,637 --> 00:12:57,557
the Fiend Battle Team with you!

269
00:13:04,598 --> 00:13:05,238
What is the sound?

270
00:13:10,877 --> 00:13:11,637
What happened outside of the city?

271
00:13:23,117 --> 00:13:23,598
You...

272
00:13:23,918 --> 00:13:25,158
It's a sandstorm.

273
00:13:25,557 --> 00:13:26,278
Go back immediately.

274
00:13:27,437 --> 00:13:28,158
Don't squeeze.

275
00:13:31,117 --> 00:13:32,077
Find a place to hide.

276
00:13:32,117 --> 00:13:33,077
Hide now! Hurry up!

277
00:13:33,077 --> 00:13:34,117
Hurry up!

278
00:13:34,158 --> 00:13:34,757
Hide!

279
00:13:35,877 --> 00:13:36,557
Ou Si Ke.

280
00:13:50,637 --> 00:13:51,238
Master.

281
00:13:53,238 --> 00:13:53,798
Tang San.

282
00:13:54,598 --> 00:13:55,117
Master.

283
00:13:55,117 --> 00:13:55,677
Wu.

284
