414
00:24:32,998 --> 00:24:34,797
She will die
if she knocks on the wall.

415
00:24:39,998 --> 00:24:41,557
Hold on tightly. I will rush into it.

416
00:24:42,118 --> 00:24:43,397
You want to rush into the storm and save her?

417
00:24:43,838 --> 00:24:44,797
