449
00:27:51,437 --> 00:27:52,317
Hurry! Get in.

450
00:27:55,638 --> 00:27:56,238
Are you all right?

451
00:27:58,317 --> 00:28:00,157
Boss, did anyone come?

452
00:28:00,797 --> 00:28:01,677
The sandstorm is here.

453
00:28:01,917 --> 00:28:03,277
No one would come and stay.

454
00:28:03,277 --> 00:28:05,037
I mean my friends

455
00:28:05,157 --> 00:28:05,917
and the two teachers.

456
00:28:06,197 --> 00:28:07,118
We stayed here previously.

457
00:28:07,317 --> 00:28:08,718
No. No one came here.

458
00:28:09,677 --> 00:28:10,838
Headmaster and the others
didn't come here.

459
00:28:11,197 --> 00:28:12,197
I have to go out and look for them.

460
00:28:13,157 --> 00:28:13,797
Don't go out.

461
00:28:14,277 --> 00:28:15,838
The Sand Beast is still out there.

462
00:28:16,118 --> 00:28:16,838
Sand Beast?

463
00:28:17,077 --> 00:28:17,638
Yes.

464
00:28:17,917 --> 00:28:19,677
Can't you hear the cry of the Sand Beast?

465
00:28:19,958 --> 00:28:21,838
This sandstorm is
caused by the Sand Beast.

466
00:28:22,157 --> 00:28:23,758
But why does the Sand Beast cause the sandstorm?

467
00:28:24,358 --> 00:28:25,358
How can I know that?

468
00:28:25,878 --> 00:28:28,037
There must be someone
who provokes the Sand Beast.

469
00:28:28,677 --> 00:28:29,677
I have to go out and figure it out.

470
00:28:29,838 --> 00:28:30,677
You don't want to live?

471
00:28:31,277 --> 00:28:33,118
You stay here. If anyone comes here,

472
00:28:33,397 --> 00:28:34,397
