I can pay you.

486
00:28:56,118 --> 00:28:56,998
I'm going to rescue my companions.

487
00:28:57,197 --> 00:28:58,037
It's very safe here.

488
00:28:58,077 --> 00:28:58,958
You can just stay here.

489
00:28:59,797 --> 00:29:00,518
Please come inside.

490
00:29:00,797 --> 00:29:01,797
It's a very important matter.

491
00:29:01,797 --> 00:29:02,598
What is the important matter?

492
00:29:02,718 --> 00:29:03,638
Come in and you'll know.

493
00:29:12,157 --> 00:29:12,557
Hurry up.

494
00:29:12,557 --> 00:29:13,437
What are you doing?

495
00:29:14,598 --> 00:29:15,317
Come in and see this.

496
00:29:15,317 --> 00:29:15,998
I'm in a hurry to look for my friends.

497
00:29:21,638 --> 00:29:22,277
Who?

498
00:29:32,598 --> 00:29:34,118
They said the sandstorm
was caused by the Sand Beast.

499
00:29:34,797 --> 00:29:35,917
Could it be this one?

500
00:29:36,718 --> 00:29:38,157
The Sand Beast crying out there

501
00:29:38,277 --> 00:29:39,598
is looking for its mate.

502
00:29:39,758 --> 00:29:40,917
Maybe it's looking for this one.

503
00:29:43,157 --> 00:29:44,437
But why is it here?

504
00:29:46,118 --> 00:29:47,238
I saw it at the night market last night.

505
00:29:47,397 --> 00:29:48,358
It was playing alone.

506
00:29:48,797 --> 00:29:50,118
I thought it was an abandoned pet.

507
00:29:51,157 --> 00:29:52,598
Then I caught it and wanted to give it to others.

508
00:29:53,397 --> 00:29:55,718
When I woke up this morning, the sandstorm came.

509
00:29:56,118 --> 00:29:57,557
You dared to do this to the Sand Beast?

510
00:29:58,557 --> 00:29:59,998
I didn't know it's a Sand Beast.

511
00:30:00,317 --> 00:30:02,118
Otherwise, I wouldn't dare to do this.

512
00:30:02,838 --> 00:30:04,277
Take it out now and set it free.

513
00:30:06,358 --> 00:30:08,797
You can help me to get out of the city,

514
00:30:09,197 --> 00:30:10,758
and we secretly set it free outside of the city.

515
00:30:11,118 --> 00:30:11,917
Then we will be all right.

516
00:30:11,998 --> 00:30:13,277
You won't be able to leave here with it beside you.

517
00:30:13,718 --> 00:30:15,157
There's a Sand Beast outside.

518
00:30:15,277 --> 00:30:16,037
What could we do then?

519
00:30:17,638 --> 00:30:20,077
Take it and this guy out to the street.

520
00:30:20,478 --> 00:30:22,917
When the Sand Beast
finds its mate and also the culprit,

521
00:30:23,077 --> 00:30:24,437
the sandstorm will probably stop.

522
00:30:24,518 --> 00:30:25,397
Then I'm doomed.

523
00:30:26,238 --> 00:30:27,878
You should bear the consequences.

524
00:30:28,077 --> 00:30:28,758
Enough.

525
00:30:29,238 --> 00:30:30,518
She just wanted to scare you. Don't worry.

526
00:30:30,838 --> 00:30:31,718
I didn't scare him.

527
00:30:33,557 --> 00:30:35,118
Send this young beast to the street.

528
00:30:35,557 --> 00:30:36,838
Don't let other Sand Beasts discover it.

529
00:30:37,998 --> 00:30:38,478
Right.

530
00:30:38,917 --> 00:30:40,358
Tang San, are you here?

531
00:30:42,638 --> 00:30:43,197
Wang Sheng?

532
00:30:47,557 --> 00:30:48,077
Wang Sheng.

533
00:30:48,838 --> 00:30:49,718
It's great that you're here.

534
00:30:50,277 --> 00:30:51,358
We encountered the sandstorm

535
00:30:51,518 --> 00:30:52,277
on the way.

536
00:30:52,518 --> 00:30:53,718
Otherwise, we'd have arrived earlier.

537
00:30:56,317 --> 00:30:57,118
What's the matter?

538
00:30:57,998 --> 00:30:59,317
The captain is asking for your whereabouts.

539
00:31:00,157 --> 00:31:01,598
Let me introduce to you

540
00:31:02,157 --> 00:31:04,598
the captain of the Fiend Battle Team,

541
00:31:05,718 --> 00:31:06,478
Meng Li.

542
00:31:15,437 --> 00:31:16,277
They are all your friends?

543
00:31:18,397 --> 00:31:19,077
More or less.

544
00:31:19,397 --> 00:31:20,718
Since all of you are Soul Masters,
you can work together.

545
00:31:21,478 --> 00:31:22,437
All of you are Soul Masters, right?

546
00:31:23,397 --> 00:31:24,838
I'm Ma Xiu Nuo from Tian Dou City.

547
00:31:25,358 --> 00:31:26,317
I hire you to send me off the city.

548
00:31:26,437 --> 00:31:27,277
You can tell the price as you wish.

549
00:31:27,718 --> 00:31:30,838
Tian Dou City. Let us tell the price?

550
00:31:32,277 --> 00:31:34,238
Yes. No matter how many
Gold Soul Coins you want.

551
00:31:35,037 --> 00:31:37,437
So generous. You come from the royal family?

552
00:31:37,518 --> 00:31:39,238
You're right. My dad is an officer in the palace.

553
00:31:39,518 --> 00:31:40,437
You can believe me.

554
00:31:45,197 --> 00:31:48,238
Does the royal family even need to hire us?

555
00:31:51,437 --> 00:31:52,118
Why are you laughing?

556
00:31:58,917 --> 00:31:59,998
The sandstorm is still raging.

557
00:32:00,317 --> 00:32:01,718
Should we engage in an internal conflict
at this point?

558
00:32:09,677 --> 00:32:10,838
All of them have Quadruple Soul Rings.

559
00:32:11,397 --> 00:32:12,598
The team is really strong.

560
00:32:13,037 --> 00:32:15,718
He's from the royal family.
So this is not an internal conflict!

561
00:32:22,157 --> 00:32:23,397
I'm not sure if I've offended you.

562
00:32:23,917 --> 00:32:25,598
Kill him.

563
00:32:25,998 --> 00:32:27,557
Stop! I can stop the sandstorm.

564
00:32:46,118 --> 00:32:47,157
You've made the right decision not to leave.

565
00:32:47,758 --> 00:32:48,397
Later,

566
00:32:48,718 --> 00:32:49,518
hold on longer in the battle,

567
00:32:50,077 --> 00:32:50,917
and you will pass the test.

568
00:32:51,157 --> 00:32:53,157
Then we will be on the same team.

569
00:32:54,478 --> 00:32:55,478
You're looking for me.

570
00:32:55,998 --> 00:32:57,077
What does it have to do with him?

571
00:32:57,718 --> 00:32:58,518
The captain gave the order

572
00:32:58,797 --> 00:32:59,677
to kill him.

573
00:33:01,157 --> 00:33:02,437
That's too extreme, Wang Sheng.

574
00:33:02,638 --> 00:33:03,998
Keep your voice down or you will die.

575
00:33:11,277 --> 00:33:12,397
Look at this.

576
00:33:13,238 --> 00:33:14,998
He caught the young beast

577
00:33:15,718 --> 00:33:16,838
and caused its mother to get mad,

578
00:33:17,598 --> 00:33:19,077
which in turn caused this sandstorm.

579
00:33:19,797 --> 00:33:20,437
He is

580
00:33:21,037 --> 00:33:22,557
the culprit who caused this disaster.

581
00:33:23,277 --> 00:33:24,238
I've said

582
00:33:25,718 --> 00:33:27,197
that those from the royal family

583
00:33:28,197 --> 00:33:29,157
don't come with a good intention.

584
00:33:29,557 --> 00:33:30,397
This is the evidence.

585
00:33:31,277 --> 00:33:32,358
I didn't intend to do that.

586
00:33:33,437 --> 00:33:34,478
This is my first time coming to Xi Si City.

587
00:33:35,157 --> 00:33:36,518
I don't know about Sand Beasts.

588
00:33:37,197 --> 00:33:38,677
This is your deliberate arrangement.

589
00:33:38,998 --> 00:33:41,077
You wish to destroy
the whole Xi Si City with the sandstorm.

590
00:33:42,157 --> 00:33:44,518
I don't have the intention.
If I had really wanted to do so,

591
00:33:45,037 --> 00:33:46,557
I wouldn't have stayed here.

592
00:33:48,638 --> 00:33:50,157
I'll give you a chance now.

593
00:33:50,638 --> 00:33:51,118
Say it.

594
00:33:52,077 --> 00:33:54,118
Bring it out of the yard

595
00:33:54,677 --> 00:33:56,878
and find its mate
to let the sandstorm recede.

596
00:33:57,238 --> 00:33:57,998
Even if I can find it,

597
00:33:58,958 --> 00:33:59,958
I will die

598
00:34:00,598 --> 00:34:01,557
once the Sand Beast gets crazy.

599
00:34:02,197 --> 00:34:04,518
Otherwise, you will die now!

600
00:34:07,797 --> 00:34:08,838
Maybe it can go out by itself

601
00:34:09,518 --> 00:34:10,557
without my assistance.

602
00:34:10,638 --> 00:34:11,397
You can't understand human words?

603
00:34:12,118 --> 00:34:12,838
There are two options. Pick one!

604
00:34:13,718 --> 00:34:14,718
You bring it out on your own

605
00:34:15,117 --> 00:34:16,597
or die now.

606
00:34:19,518 --> 00:34:20,357
I'll go for him.

607
00:34:26,197 --> 00:34:27,117
Are you close to him?

608
00:34:27,318 --> 00:34:28,357
Why do you want to die for him?

609
00:34:28,998 --> 00:34:29,877
I heard from Wang Sheng

610
00:34:30,437 --> 00:34:31,278
that you are his friend.

611
00:34:32,478 --> 00:34:34,597
Yes, we're from the same school.

612
00:34:34,917 --> 00:34:36,357
Then why do you help an outsider?

613
00:34:37,078 --> 00:34:38,278
The Sand Beast has gone mad.

614
00:34:39,157 --> 00:34:40,798
If I don't help him, the situation will get worse.

615
00:34:41,357 --> 00:34:42,397
It's his own mistake,

616
00:34:43,197 --> 00:34:44,917
so he has to bear with it.

617
00:34:46,078 --> 00:34:46,958
He is too timid.

618
00:34:48,917 --> 00:34:50,558
You mean you are brave enough?

619
00:34:51,397 --> 00:34:52,798
Someone must do it.

620
00:34:53,677 --> 00:34:54,558
I'm more suitable than him.

621
00:34:55,197 --> 00:34:55,758
Moreover,

622
00:34:56,437 --> 00:34:57,478
if the sandstorm keeps going on,

623
00:34:58,397 --> 00:34:59,437
it'll be dangerous for you too.

624
00:35:03,278 --> 00:35:03,758
All right.

625
00:35:09,478 --> 00:35:09,917
I...

626
00:35:17,637 --> 00:35:18,718
I can go on my own.

627
00:35:22,837 --> 00:35:24,478
Okay, then you have to listen to me.

628
00:35:37,478 --> 00:35:38,637
Aren't you their companion?

629
00:35:39,078 --> 00:35:39,798
Why don't you go with them?

630
